00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,080
It's all my fault. My fault!

555
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,680
Sister-in-law, it's not your fault.

556
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:08,920
Qiaonian.

557
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:09,920
What's going on?

558
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:13,440
You shouldn't be the only one who did it.

559
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,560
Where are your associates?

560
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:15,687
Bring him here.

561
00:22:16,199 --> 00:22:18,856
Chen Yannian, come out!

562
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,360
I'm the mastermind of this.

563
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:31,720
Take it out on me if you're angry.

564
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,640
Yannian, how old are you?

565
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:34,840
Are you still a child?

566
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,080
You are an adult!

567
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:38,120
How could you do such a ridiculous thing?

568
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:40,200
Even if you have a problem with your old man,

569
00:22:40,452 --> 00:22:41,600
you can't treat him like this!

570
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:43,880
Do you know what you call this?

571
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,720
This is called treason!

572
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,920
This would be frowned upon in our home town!

573
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:49,200
Heaven condemns you!

574
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,280
Sorry, Uncle Wang, Aunt Wang.

575
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:57,680
I've put you in a difficult position.

576
00:22:58,120 --> 00:22:59,080
I do this today,

577
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,520
not because of him, Chen Duxiu,

578
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,800
who didn't take enough care of my mother and us two brothers.

579
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,040
In Anqing,

580
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,520
we were not rich.

581
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,280
But at least the family has some property,

582
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:09,560
enough for our family to live on.

583
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,880
Since he doesn't care about us,

584
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,560
we won't beg him again.

585
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:13,600
We're doing this today

586
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:16,400
for the sake of our suffering family

587
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:17,480
and for

588
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:19,320
our cousin Chen Yongnian, who has been tortured because of him,

589
00:23:19,360 --> 00:23:20,880
to teach him a lesson.

590
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,080
To speak of treason,

591
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:26,520
Chen Duxiu is the one who is really

592
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:28,280
a treacherous hypocrite.

593
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,360
Yannian, you're going too far!

594
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,400
Don't talk about your father like that!

595
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:32,240
You shut up!

596
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,160
Let him speak.

597
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:34,480
Alright.

598
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:36,920
Today, in front of all my uncles and aunts,

599
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,960
I'm going to reveal the shame of our Chen family.

600
00:23:39,320 --> 00:23:40,600
Everyone please judge.

601
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:42,160
Last autumn,

602
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,120
after the failure of the Second Revolution in Anqing,

603
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:46,603
Chen Duxiu himself abandons his family and flees,

604
00:23:47,117 --> 00:23:48,441
knowing the danger,

605
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:50,160
but still left his sick grandmother

606
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,280
and our mother and son behind.

607
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,920
Ni Xichong sent his men to raid our house.

608
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,200
My sister, Yuying, sacrificed her life to block the front hall

609
00:23:57,240 --> 00:24:00,080
covering me and Qiaonian to jump out of the window.

610
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:01,920
Cousin Chen Yongnian

611
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,880
who protected his younger brother Chen Zhannian

612
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,520
was arrested for pretending to be me,

613
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:07,920
and was tortured to death.

614
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:11,920
Grandfather, who died after a long illness, was still at home

615
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:14,200
Grandmother is bedridden.

616
00:24:15,384 --> 00:24:16,591
The family rushed to Shanghai

617
00:24:17,280 --> 00:24:18,167
to find Chen Duxiu,

618
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,840
asking him to return for his father's funeral.

619
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:23,160
But he was greedy for life and death.

620
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,160
Not only did he not go back to do his filial duty,

621
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:27,400
but he instead persuaded the family

622
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,760
to wait for a few years.

623
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,920
In the eyes of others,

624
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:35,360
Chen Duxiu is a great hero of righteousness.

625
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,400
But does anyone know,

626
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,840
that this is the great hero before you?

627
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:42,440
He lived for himself

628
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:45,800
and put the lives of his parents at risk.

629
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:48,000
That's what's so treacherous.

630
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:49,160
You shut up!

631
00:24:49,280 --> 00:24:49,760
Yannian!

632
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:52,200
You have wronged your father by saying so!

633
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,000
After the Second Revolution,

634
00:24:57,560 --> 00:24:59,760
Your father risked his life to persuade Gong Zhenpeng's troops in Wuhu

635
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:03,240
to return to Anqing to fight Yuan.

636
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,160
However,

637
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:06,320
this Gong Zhenpeng arrested your father.

638
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:08,440
The notice to be executed was posted.

639
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:09,680
A matter of life and death,

640
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:10,560
your father

641
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,280
didn't even frown!

642
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:14,720
It was Liu Shuya who saved him later.

643
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:16,720
He died in Shanghai.

644
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:19,480
He was the most wanted man at the time.

645
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:21,720
A reward of one thousand yuan was offered.

646
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:22,720
At that time,

647
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:25,160
how could he possibly go back to Anqing?

648
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:31,840
Yannian. Do you know

649
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:34,400
the people who came to Shanghai to find your father?

650
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:36,920
They were sent by Ni Xichong.

651
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,880
It was a trap!

652
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,520
Your father risked his life to return for a funeral

653
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:44,160
but we stopped him.

654
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:45,155
He didn't go back.

655
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,160
In those days,

656
00:25:46,446 --> 00:25:49,357
he pointed to the picture of Ni Xichong every day and said

657
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,880
he wanted to eat his own flesh!

658
00:25:52,320 --> 00:25:54,200
But what you said about your father

659
00:25:54,560 --> 00:25:55,560
is not fair to him.

660
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,240
Then we were not wronged!

661
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:58,600
My grandfather, my grandmother,

662
00:25:58,600 --> 00:25:59,240
my mother, my cousin,

663
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:00,360
they were not wronged!

664
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,600
Was he wronged? Was he aggrieved?

665
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:06,800
It's not for us to judge.

666
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:08,360
Today, this matter

667
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,840
is not a prank

668
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:12,360
because he doesn't deserve to eat this dish.

669
00:26:13,320 --> 00:26:14,480
We did this today

670
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:16,480
as a way to explain to the family

671
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:20,000
From now on, we clear our grudges,

672
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,280
not cross each other's paths,

673
00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:22,600
and go our separate ways.

674
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,280
If you uncles and uncles feel

675
00:26:24,320 --> 00:26:26,040
that this is a prank

676
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:27,840
then we apologise to everyone

677
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:30,040
for scaring our uncles and aunts.

678
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:40,200
Aunt, we are sorry for your loss.

679
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,640
We've scared you too.

680
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,200
It was not our intention.

681
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:44,640
We don't hold a grudge against you.

682
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:46,360
Please forgive us.

683
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,006
Yannian!

684
00:26:51,655 --> 00:26:52,853
Yannian! Yannian!

685
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:59,080
By the way,

686
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:01,200
we didn't come to Shanghai to join you.

687
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:02,920
Let me put it to you this way,

688
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:03,560
we came

689
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:05,560
after we read the work-study initiative.

690
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,080
We decided to come to Shanghai to study French

691
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:10,000
and go to France to work and study.

692
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:12,080
We'll make our own way, 

693
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,160
don't worry about it.

694
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:16,840
Yannian! Qiaonian!

695
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,840
Listen to me, Yannian!

696
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:21,000
This... I... I... you say, you say...

697
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:31,040
Well, those are my sons.

698
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:34,080
Zhong Fu, how can you laugh at that?

699
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:36,040
Both sons have disowned you.

700
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:39,120
I, Chen Duxiu, have two such wonderful sons.

701
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:41,320
Why can't I laugh?

702
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:44,160
I didn't get to give my parents a final send-off,

703
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:46,120
I deserve to die for that.

704
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,440
The fact that they remembered to blame me

705
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:49,280
shows that they are humane people.

706
00:27:50,100 --> 00:27:53,040
The fact that they are willing to work hard rather than rely on me

707
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:56,040
shows that they are self-reliant and self-sufficient people.

708
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:57,440
In such a fragile world,

709
00:27:58,440 --> 00:28:00,200
aren't these two qualities

710
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:02,880
to be congratulated?

711
00:28:05,100 --> 00:28:07,720
Zhong Fu, you haven't said a word.

712
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:10,480
I'm still trying to figure out how to comfort you.

713
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,920
You, on the contrary, he's praising his son.

714
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:14,320
But what he said,

715
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:16,045
is a relief to us all.

716
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:16,927
It is.

717
00:28:16,927 --> 00:28:17,840
But Zhong Fu,

718
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:19,840
I've just been watching your two boys,

719
00:28:20,320 --> 00:28:21,520
they're not normal.

720
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:23,317
They will be great men in the future.

721
00:28:23,448 --> 00:28:24,041
That's right!

722
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,800
These two children have high ambitions!

723
00:28:52,324 --> 00:28:53,164
Brother Mengzou.

724
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:54,760
Apologies to you.

725
00:28:55,059 --> 00:28:56,161
You're not stingy

726
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:59,640
with your lotus leaf and yellow cow's trotters.

727
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:01,760
I accept, I accept.

728
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,400
Let's switch!

729
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,360
You're dirty. You eat this.

730
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,080
No, no, no.

731
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,360
Didn't you hear what my son said?

732
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:08,640
I don't deserve to eat this dish.

733
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,400
There are other dishes here.

734
00:29:12,600 --> 00:29:13,560
So, so, so, let's do it!

735
00:29:13,846 --> 00:29:14,140
Come on!

736
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:14,760
Come, come, come!

737
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,240
Please, please!

738
00:29:15,320 --> 00:29:15,840
Have a drink!

739
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:26,360
[Waseda University dormitory, Japan]

740
00:29:30,613 --> 00:29:33,439
[Li Dazhao, styled Shou Chang, student at Waseda University]

741
00:29:44,360 --> 00:29:45,640
In 1915,

742
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,280
the twenty-six-year-old Li Dazhao

743
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:51,360
wrote the article "Misanthropy and Self-awareness"

744
00:29:52,040 --> 00:29:55,320
against Chen Duxiu's "Patriotism and Self-consciousness",

745
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:56,160
as challenge.

746
00:29:57,840 --> 00:29:59,360
With a positive and optimistic attitude,

747
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:01,400
he urged the nation to rise

748
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:04,040
and join the movement against Yuan.

749
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,720
Improving the spirit of nationalism

750
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:10,520
and enouraging patriotism;

751
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:13,000
by this time, Li Dazhao

752
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:14,760
had become

753
00:30:14,800 --> 00:30:17,800
a thoroughgoing anti-feudal activist.

754
00:30:36,615 --> 00:30:37,803
Shou Chang.

755
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:39,600
What are you doing?

756
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,283
You scared the hell out of me.

757
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,647
Mr. Xing Yan, what brings you here?

758
00:30:47,410 --> 00:30:47,970
Have a seat!

759
00:30:47,970 --> 00:30:49,640
I'm going back home, just wanted to see you.

760
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:52,080
Please sit!

761
00:30:53,560 --> 00:30:55,320
What's the matter? What's the panic?

762
00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:56,280
Did something happen?

763
00:30:58,040 --> 00:30:59,004
I may have recently become

764
00:30:59,004 --> 00:31:00,841
a thorn in the side

765
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,519
of some Japanese students.

766
00:31:02,519 --> 00:31:03,852
[Zhang Tuzhao, styled Xing Yan, revolutionary exiled to Japan]

767
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:04,480
They often use the pretext of supervising my classes

768
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:05,640
to pick fights,

769
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:06,720
destroying my manuscripts.

770
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:08,360
So when I hear a knock at the door,

771
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:10,200
my first thought was to hide the manuscript.

772
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:17,480
You attend a variety of events and make a lot of appearances,

773
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:19,400
it is inevitable that you will be watched.

774
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,200
Shou Chang.

775
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:24,800
I've heard the school has a lot to say about you.

776
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:28,800
Japanese universities are very strict in their administration.

777
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,640
You need to be careful.

778
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,614
[Gan Yihao, student at Waseda University]

779
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:30,920
You have to find 

780
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:33,760
a way to make the most of both your studies and the revolution.

781
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:38,921
I heard you. I am organizing

782
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:41,200
the Chinese Students Association in Japan.

783
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:43,840
And I'm planning to talk to Yihan

784
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,400
to start a magazine called "Minyi" (Rule of people's will)

785
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:47,360
as a publication of the association.

786
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:48,840
Inspired by the "Jiayin", 

787
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,640
the "Minyi" also opposes

788
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:51,240
and resists Yuan Shikai's authoritarian politics

789
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:54,080
by commenting and discussing the current situation,

790
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,800
to foster a modern civilization

791
00:31:55,840 --> 00:31:57,160
and promote the awakening of the people.

792
00:31:57,480 --> 00:31:59,240
It did make me miss a lot of classes,

793
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:00,800
but the revolutionary situation at the moment

794
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:02,160
is in full swing.

795
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:03,600
I had a really hard time choosing.

796
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:04,960
This is not acceptable.

797
00:32:05,282 --> 00:32:06,080
In my opinion,

798
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:08,600
academics are also the essence of the revolution.

799
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:10,080
Now that you are in the door,

800
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:11,800
you must get your diploma.

801
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:13,160
Otherwise, it'll be a shame.

802
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:17,360
In fact, the usual is doing quite well.

803
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,400
In 11 subjects last school year,

804
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:20,160
he scored 736 points.

805
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:21,440
In politics and economics,

806
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,760
out of 106 students

807
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:24,640
he ranked in the top 40.

808
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,320
Because he's never had a high school education

809
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,920
and went straight to undergraduate school,

810
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:30,880
that's a good grade, it's not bad.

811
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,920
Just third place, it's a shame.

812
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:35,200
Third place is really not bad.

813
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:36,520
You're good and you're willing to work hard.

814
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,120
Academics are not a problem for you.

815
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,040
Compliance with school rules is your problem.

816
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:44,080
I'm really at a bit of a loss now.

817
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:47,280
What is more important, the revolution or school?

818
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:49,040
It's really hard for me to choose.

819
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,480
You put yourself out on a hot day,

820
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,520
locked up in your dorm room studying.

821
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:55,240
That means you know the difference.

